(14, 'Resident Evil 9 Rumors Hint At A 28-Year First For The Franchise ', '<p>The Resident Evil franchise hasn\'t been afraid to shake things up over the years, and a rumor about the next new game in the series points to another franchise first on its way. Although every game is interconnected by unifying elements involving deadly viruses, various forms of the ruthless Umbrella corporation, and plenty of horrific enemies, there\'s a lot of room to do different things within that overarching lore. It\'s easy to jump into any mainline game and get a complete experience of its own, and the unique flavor provided by each can satisfy many different preferences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keeping with this idea, there\'s been a good bit of setting-hopping in the series to date. From the iconic Midwestern locale of Raccoon City in the original game to the Eastern European flair of Resident Evil Village, fear has been found in many different corners of the globe. Fixing the unique lens of Resident Evil on new cultural inspirations is always interesting, even accounting for some arguable missteps in the past, and the rumored Resident Evil 9 is purportedly moving to a completely fresh one.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Resident Evil 9 Might Be Set In Southeast Asia</h2>\r\n<h4><i>A Rumor Points To A Location Inspired By Singapore</i></h4>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://static1.srcdn.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/resident-evil-4-remake-leon-1.jpg?q=49&fit=contain&w=750&h=415&dpr=2\" alt=\"resident-evil-4-remake-leon-1\">\r\n\r\n<p>As noted in a Reddit post from No1PiggyOnTheBlock, leaker Dusk Golem responded to a query on X (formerly Twitter) to allege that Resident Evil 9 will shift to a Southeast Asian setting. Like previous fictionalized settings in the franchise, Resident Evil 9 will reportedly use its own fictitious town on an island modeled after Singapore. It\'s a far cry from anything the series has explored before, as Resident Evil 6\'s dip into China remains the only major exploration of an Asian setting that the games have yet offered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Like all rumors, this one shouldn\'t be taken as hard fact, and Dusk Golem has a somewhat mixed track record overall. The leaker\'s 2021 claims of a third Resident Evil Revelations game called Outrage (still accessible on Dusk Golem\'s account) never panned out, and some information that they spread regarding Resident Evil Village similarly turned out to be mistaken. A 50/50 community reliability ranking on Reddit points to the fact that Dusk Golem hasn\'t always been wrong, however, so it\'s worth considering as a legitimate possibility.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Singapore Would Be A Cool Resident Evil Setting</h2>\r\n<h4><i>Southeast Asia Isn\'t Always Represented In Games</i></h4>\r\n<img src=\"https://static1.srcdn.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/resident-evil-4-ashley-graham.jpg?q=70&fit=crop&w=825&dpr=1\" alt=\"resident-evil-4-ashley-graham\">\r\n\r\n<p>A Singapore-inspired setting for Resident Evil 9 could be a cool addition to the series, as games that explore Southeast Asia are generally few and far between. 2022\'s A Space for the Unbound stood out as an affecting look at the life of teenagers in Indonesia, and although Resident Evil 9 may not be as carefully intimate of a game, it could boast a similar appeal of showcasing a culture that doesn\'t get a major spotlight in video gaming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There\'s nothing wrong with Resident Evil revisiting tried and true settings, but after a succession of remakes, it\'s nice to see that the next game may be looking elsewhere. It\'s also a bit surprising that the series is turning to Singapore before ever visiting Japan, considering that the games come out of a Japanese studio. The company might just like exploring other avenues when it comes to Resident Evil and leaving the closer-to-home approach to titles like the upcoming Kunitsu-Gami: Path of the Goddess, but there\'s also the possibility that Resident Evil will have its homecoming in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It shouldn\'t be too long now before official news clarifies what players can expect from Resident Evil 9, although gratification in that regard might not be immediate. The latest update indicates a possible internal delay for Resident Evil 9 that could push the game back a bit, information once again provided by Dusk Golem. Regardless of what the future of Resident Evil ends up looking like, it\'s exciting to consider different places that the series could go, and a setting inspired by Singapore would definitely be an interesting option.</p>\r\n\r\n', 'Ben Brosofsky', '2024-05-13', 'resident-evil.jpg', 'https://screenrant.com/resident-evil-9-setting-southeast-asia-singapore-rumor/', 4),
(16, 'Grandpa and Grandma Turn Young Again Anime Releases Special OP Theme MV', '<p>\r\n    The official website for the ongoing spring 2024 TV anime Grandpa and Grandma Turn Young Again has posted a special music video featuring its opening theme song \"Ojiichan Atashi ga Obaachan\" (You aa, I am Grandma), performed by singer-songwriter Koresawa.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n    The clip, accompanied by the emotional song, looks back on the love story of Shozo and Ine, focusing on scenes from the first five episodes of the TV anime that has aired since April.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>Grandpa and Grandma Turn Young Again special music video</i></h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZUUP9uu8jxc?si=qIqGazxg6wb_7y3B\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Grandpa and Grandma Turn Young Again anime creditless opening movie</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n    <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SNRH8aIo0Jo?si=yfQOF1P-GTtLSwv9\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Ojiichan Atashi ga Obaachan\"</strong> is incKoresawa\'s latest third digital mini album <strong>\"Hibi AiaI\"</strong> released on March 6, 2024</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<iframe style=\"border-radius:12px\" src=\"https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/7A82mHia7alj13QXGc6MDQ?utm_source=generator\" width=\"60%\" height=\"300\" frameBorder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Koresawa \"Kimi ga Ojiichan Atashi ga Obaachan\" music video</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n    <iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sZvcG_97mmE?si=JcwK_Bm-Xxo208y8\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n    The TV anime adaptation of Kagiri Araido\'s romantic comedy manga Grandpa and Grandma Turn Young Again premiered in Japan on April 7. Crunchyroll is streaming the GEKKOU-produced series for members in North America, Central America, South America, Europe, Africa, Oceania, the Middle East and CIS.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Crunchyroll describes the series:</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>After eating a mysterious apple from their farm, an elderly pair of lovebirds, Shouzou and Ine, experience a miraculous transformation into their younger selves. Despite their newfound youth and beauty, the two continue in their cute senior ways. Witness an enduring bond that\'s stronger and more precious than ever before.</blockquote>', 'Mikikazu Komatsu', '2024-05-13', 'grandpa&grandma.jpg', 'https://www.crunchyroll.com/news/latest/2024/5/13/grandpa-and-grandma-turn-young-again-anime-releases-special-opening-theme-music-video', 1),
